，将会产生很大的积极影响。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:49:04.000Z","msg":"你個國家冇信用架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b5dfd8bcdabe74fed585db03bea9d94c27dfbc","tid":1494334,"uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"一個諗盡辦法去呃國民錢既國家"},{"pid":"8f486271cb0918fb37237084464cbb58e0c55cc6","tid":1494334,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:04:43.000Z","msg":"成篇文都除左講會出加密貨幣外其他都唔明講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a5a38e276b3a77b06956361672ee86b81124b9","tid":1494334,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:20:12.000Z","msg":"不斷入錢但個餘額都會慢慢跌番0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399991514f0fb0f7ef71ae5210eef67c4c3ec8a5","tid":1494334,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:20:59.000Z","msg":"撈錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec859821d439a72749dd94c8be9f802d91342c3","tid":1494334,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">与此同时，央行数字货币还能够在反洗钱、反恐融资方面提供帮助</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要控制者"},{"pid":"f4034d54f3fb92d119e6e531a7a62cc4c46ccfe6","tid":1494334,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a683ca23d8cddcddf450e3942894e87d96d3937","tid":1494334,"uid":28068,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"如果真係出<br />\n證明離死期不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:24:53.000Z","msg":"窮撚到要gen錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d7059b244c66dfd3db70f68f694d5934ff2b87","tid":1494334,"uid":218504,"like":0,